<!doctype html><html lang="ko"><head><meta charset="utf-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1"><title><%=title%></title><link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/style.css"><style>.apply-wrap{max-width:860px;margin:40px auto;padding:0 18px}.apply-card{background:#101525;border:1px solid #29324f;border-radius:22px;padding:28px;color:#f5f7ff}.apply-card h1{margin:0 0 10px;font-size:34px}.apply-card p{color:#c8d0e8}.apply-form{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px;margin-top:22px}.apply-form input,.apply-form textarea,.apply-form select{background:#070b15;color:#fff;border:1px solid #29324f;border-radius:12px;padding:13px}.apply-form textarea{grid-column:1/3;min-height:130px;resize:vertical}.apply-form .full{grid-column:1/3}.guide{grid-column:1/3;background:#080d18;border:1px dashed #39466c;border-radius:14px;padding:14px;color:#c8d0e8;line-height:1.7}.apply-form button{grid-column:1/3;height:52px;border:0;border-radius:14px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#ff3fb4,#10d9ff);color:#fff;font-weight:900;font-size:17px}.done{background:#082316;border:1px solid #1fa463;padding:18px;border-radius:14px;margin-top:18px}@media(max-width:700px){.apply-form{grid-template-columns:1fr}.apply-form textarea,.apply-form .full,.guide,.apply-form button{grid-column:1}}</style></head><body><header class="top"><a class="brand" href="/">서비스 디렉터리</a><nav><a href="/">홈</a><a href="/advertise">광고문의</a><a href="/apply">입점신청</a></nav></header><main class="apply-wrap"><section class="apply-card"><h1><%=title%></h1><p><%=type==='apply'?'업체 정보를 보내주시면 관리자가 확인 후 등록을 도와드립니다.':'프리미엄 배너, 추천업체, 광고 노출 문의를 남겨주세요.'%></p><% if(done){ %><div class="done">신청이 정상 접수되었습니다. 관리자가 확인 후 연락드립니다.</div><% } %><% if(error){ %><div class="done" style="background:#2a1010;border-color:#ff6b6b">오류: <%=error%></div><% } %><form method="post" action="/inquiry" enctype="multipart/form-data" class="apply-form"><input type="hidden" name="type" value="<%=type%>"><input name="company_name" placeholder="업체명" required><input name="name" placeholder="담당자명"><input name="phone" placeholder="연락처" required><input name="kakao" placeholder="카카오톡 링크 또는 ID"><% if(type==='apply'){ %><input name="category" placeholder="업종" required><input name="region" placeholder="지역" required><% }else{ %><input name="email" placeholder="이메일"><select name="category"><option value="프리미엄배너">프리미엄 배너</option><option value="추천업체">추천업체</option><option value="일반광고">일반 광고</option></select><% } %><textarea name="content" placeholder="문의내용 또는 업체소개를 입력해주세요" required></textarea><% if(type==='apply'){ %><div class="guide"><b>대표 이미지 업로드</b><br>권장 사이즈: 800 x 600px / JPG, PNG, GIF / 5MB 이하</div><input class="full" type="file" name="main_image" accept="image/png,image/jpeg,image/gif"><div class="guide"><b>배너 이미지 업로드</b><br>권장 사이즈: 1200 x 300px / JPG, PNG, GIF / 5MB 이하</div><input class="full" type="file" name="banner_image" accept="image/png,image/jpeg,image/gif"><% } %><button>신청하기</button></form></section></main></body></html>